QuestData.Title: Elune's Fire
QuestData.Description: We need special flame for ritual. We need Elune's fire.$B$BHoroo's spirit wanders east of here. Horoo carries torch of Elune. Bring here so spirits rest.$B$BAroom thanks you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Obtain Elune's Torch from Horoo the Flamekeeper.
QuestData.RewardText: <Aroom lets out a long low-pitched hoot.>$B$BFinally kin may rest.
